org.gbif.api.model.common

Class DOI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.common.DOI

  • public class DOI
extends Object
    Class representing a single Digital Object Identifier (DOI) breaking it down to a prefix and suffix. For the syntax of DOI names see the DOI Handbook. All parsing is case insensitive and resulting components will all be upper cased.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  DOI.Deserializer
      Deserializes a DOI from various string based formats.
      static class  DOI.Serializer
      Serializes a DOI as doi name with a doi: scheme.
